==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Offprint
<hw>Off`print"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Off</ets>
+ <ets>print</ets>.]</ety> <def>To reprint (as an excerpt); <as>as, the
articles of some magazines are <ex>offprinted</ex> from other
magazines</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Offprint</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Offprint
<hw>Off"print`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A reprint or
excerpt.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>off-putting</ent>⟦br⟧
